sequenceDiagram
    participant O as RL Training Loop
    participant I as Inference Server (Active Model)
    participant G as Generator
    participant E as Environment & Grader
    participant D as Dataset
    participant T as Trainer (Model Updater)

    Note over I,T: Physical separation of Inference Server and Trainer
    
    loop For K Iterations
        O->>G: 1. Request Batch of N episodes
        
        rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
            Note over G,E: Generation Phase (on Inference Server)
            loop N times
                G->>D: 2. Fetch Prompt
                D-->>G: Prompt
                G->>I: 3a. Sample Actions
                I-->>G: Tool Call Intention
                G->>E: 3b. Execute Tools & Grade
                E-->>G: Observation & Reward
                Note over G: Trajectory Completed
            end
        end
        
        G-->>O: 4. Return Batch of N rows
        
        O->>T: 5. Submit Batch and Model M_i for training
        Note over T: Trainer computes Loss, runs Backprop,<br/>and updates model weights
        T-->>O: 6. Return Updated Model M_{i+1}
        
        Note over O,I: === WEIGHT SYNC ===
        O->>I: 7. Sync M_{i+1} weights to Inference Server
    end
